{
  "title": "Smoky Gooey Japanese White Cornmeal Fold",
  "description": "A paleo-friendly post-workout dish featuring gooey and smoky flavors from smoked paprika and white cornmeal, perfect for satisfying your cravings after a workout.",
  "cuisine": "Japanese",
